### GET ALL USERS
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users

### GET USER BY ID (valid)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/1

### GET USER BY ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/99999

### CREATE USER (valid)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "username": "newuser123",
  "password": "supersecret123"
}

### CREATE USER (invalid email)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "username": "abc",
  "password": "password123"
}

### CREATE USER (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### UPDATE USER (valid)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/45
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

### UPDATE USER (forbidden)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nope@example.com"
}

